<section id="index-knownproblems">
    <title>Known Problems</title>
    <para>The following problems and limitations are known to exist for WS MDS Index Service at the
        time of the <replaceable role="entity">version</replaceable> release:</para>

    <section>
        <title>Limitations</title>
        <indexterm type="index"><primary>limitations</primary></indexterm>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <simpara>The WS-MDS Index Service currently keeps the entire set of index data in memory; the size of the index is thus limited by the amount of memory available to the Glob us container.</simpara>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>

    </section>

